From: STGR Browser Team <dev@stgr-browser.dev>
Date: Tue, 2 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: Tab Groups implementation with visual hierarchy and nesting

Implements tab groups for the vertical sidebar:
- Create, rename, delete, recolor groups
- Add/remove tabs via drag-drop onto group headers and context menu
- Collapsible group headers with chevron, color dot, name, tab count, close button
- Grouped tabs indented 18px within the sidebar
- Expand/collapse with smooth animation
- Context menu: "New Group with Tab", "Remove from Group", "Add to Group" submenu
- Group context menu: rename, select all, change color, ungroup all, delete
- Ctrl+Shift+G to collapse all groups
- Persists groups via stgr.tabGroups.data pref (JSON)
- Tab-group membership persisted via stgrGroupId attribute on <tab> element
- Panel guard prevents re-render after destruction
- RTL-aware CSS

